# Architecture & Tenancy

## موجودیت‌ها (ADR-002, ADR-017 — نقض ممنوع)

```
Platform → Tenant → Branch, Staff, TenantCustomer
User (platform identity, phone unique)
 ├── Staff[] (per tenant — B2B)
 └── GlobalCustomer? (B2C profile)
         └── TenantCustomer (junction — NOT direct to User)
```

- Customer **زیر Branch نیست**
- `phone` فقط روی **User** — Staff/GlobalCustomer از join
- Staff و Customer می‌توانند same User/phone — session جدا
- یک User می‌تواند Staff در چند tenant باشد

## Module System

- `modules/core/` — همیشه فعال (tenant, rbac, auth, audit, settings)
- `modules/installments/` — ماژول ۱
- هر endpoint ماژولی: `@RequireModule('installments')` + plan entitlement

## قرارگیری کد

| نوع | مسیر |
|-----|------|
| Entity / Rule | `packages/domain/{module}/` |
| Use Case | `packages/application/{module}/` |
| Repository | `packages/infrastructure/persistence/` |
| Zod DTO | `packages/contracts/{module}/` |

## Multi-Tenant

```typescript
// ✅ EVERY tenant-scoped query
where: { tenantId: ctx.tenantId, ... }

// ❌ NEVER trust client tenant_id without JWT verification
```

- Repository layer + middleware — defense in depth
- Integration test: cross-tenant **must fail**

## Events

- Side effects → Domain Event → Outbox → Worker
- Handlers idempotent
- ماژول‌ها via event — not direct entity import

## Settings vs Invariants

- **Settings:** schema keys only (`settings.schema.ts`)
- **Invariants:** domain code (paid never deleted, status transitions)

